						               													<description>Once upon a time there was a Wolf trying to catch three little pigs without any luck. That's a well known story from the past, and now the wolves and the pigs compete every year in an annual houses build &amp;amp; demolition festival in the wood of Piggy Forest!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Piggy Forest is a collaborative card game where the players must build houses of different materials (straw, wood and stone) inside of which they must later place the pigs (not three like the original story but nine). Three different wolves will appear destroying the houses, so the players must play together by exchanging building materials and characters from their hands. Other special characters called &amp;quot;protectors&amp;quot; also appear (they will help to win the game).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a card game for family, kids and friends, with solo play system and 9 extra ways to play!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you miss this exciting battle? The Piggy Forest Team vs The Wolf Gang!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
